wiki.summary: “My Mind & Me” is a song featured in Gomez’s documentary also titled “My Mind & Me” which was released on November 4, 2022, exclusively on Apple TV. The documentary was initially rumored to be released sometime in 2022. On September 8, Selena Gomez tweeted and confirmed the documentary would “come soon”. A little over a month later, Gomez officially announced the documentary’s release on October 10, which reflects on the past 6 years of Gomez’s personal life, including her battles with her mental health and her diagnoses. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: “My Mind & Me” is a song featured in Gomez’s documentary also titled “My Mind & Me” which was released on November 4, 2022, exclusively on Apple TV. The documentary was initially rumored to be released sometime in 2022. On September 8, Selena Gomez tweeted and confirmed the documentary would “come soon”. A little over a month later, Gomez officially announced the documentary’s release on October 10, which reflects on the past 6 years of Gomez’s personal life, including her battles with her mental health and her diagnoses. The date of the announcement was also the day on which World Mental Health Day is celebrated, which further emphasizes the idea of the documentary. Snippets of the song were scattered throughout the trailer, while its lyric content further dives into her battles. Under the post, Selena Gomez then went on to tease the song, sharing that the song would be “coming soon!!“. Read more on Last.fm.
